data.description: Welcome to your desert paradise! Nestled in the heart of Florence, this beautiful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a tranquil and spacious retreat from the bustling world. With its stunning curb appeal and thoughtful interior, it's a must-see property. Everything around the home is new or has been replaced over the past few years. All New Plumbing, Newer fixtures, New Partial Paint, front windows have been replaced as well. Not only do you get a worry free home but you get community filled with amazing amenities and events. Let's not forget you get to own the LAND! Come stop by before this stunning home is gone.
